PrecisAppointment of ROBERT G. KILPATRICK, of Smithers, British Columbia, as Judge of the Nunavut Court of Justice, effective April 1, 1999, as well as Judge of the Court of Appeal of Nunavut, Judge of the Court of Appeal for the Northwest Territories, and Judge of the Court of Appeal for the Yukon Territory, during his tenure of office as Judge of the Nunavut Court of Justice.
